'''湖木教会'''（Lakewood Church）是一个[[基督教|基督教]][[灵恩派|灵恩派]]的[[非宗派教会|非宗派]]{{link-en|巨型教會|Megachurch|巨型教会}}，位于美国德克萨斯州[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]。它是美国最大的教会，平均每周参加聚会的人数达到约52,000人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://christianpost.com/news/joel-osteens-lakewood-church-ranked-americas-largest-megachurch-with-52k-in-attendance-169279 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-28 |archive-date=2016-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125045153/http://www.christianpost.com/news/joel-osteens-lakewood-church-ranked-americas-largest-megachurch-with-52k-in-attendance-169279/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。16,800个座位的湖木教会总堂，每周举行四次英语聚会和两次西班牙语聚会<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lakewood.cc/Services/Pages/LakewoodChurchServices.aspx|publisher=Lakewood Church|title=Services|4=|access-date=2016-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201101520/http://www.lakewood.cc/SERVICES/Pages/LakewoodChurchServices.aspx|archive-date=2010-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=USA>{{cite news|title=America's largest church opens in former arena|work=USA Today|date=July 14, 2005|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-07-14-largest-church_x.htm|accessdate=2009-07-21|archive-date=2009-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090730024746/http://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-07-14-largest-church_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[约尔·欧斯汀|约尔·欧斯汀]]是湖木教会的主任牧师。

==历史==
[[File:Joel_Osteen_at_Lakewood_Church.JPG|thumb]]
湖木教会是由约翰·欧斯汀夫妇在1959年5月10日母亲节，在休斯敦东北部一个废弃的饲料店内建立的。<ref name=southerncrossroads67>{{cite book |editor-last=Conser Jr |editor-first=Walter H. |editor2=Rodger M. Payne | title =Southern Crossroads:Perspectives on Religion and Culture|url=https://archive.org/details/footballphilosop00aust | publisher =The University Press of Kentucky| year =2008| pages =[https://archive.org/details/footballphilosop00aust/page/n77 67]–8| isbn = 978-0-8131-2494-0}}</ref>约翰是[[美南浸信会|美南浸信会]]牧师，但是他在经历灵浸后，湖木教会去掉了名字中的“浸信会”，成为一个灵恩派的非宗派教会。从一开始，湖木教会已经具有种族包容性。到1979年，教会出席人数超过五千人，在[[五旬节|五旬节]]派和灵恩派中变得突出。1999年1月23日，约翰·奥斯汀死于[[心肌梗死|心肌梗死]]，他的小儿子约尔·欧斯汀成为牧师。

在约尔·欧斯汀带领下，湖木教会的会众增加了近五倍。<ref name="msnbc.msn.com">{{cite web| title = Nation’s largest church opens in stadium| work = MSNBC| url = http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/8565629/| accessdate = 2007-02-25| archive-date = 2007-02-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070224125223/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/8565629/| dead-url = no}}</ref> 每周出席人数增加到3万，遂决定从东休斯敦路7317号<ref>"[https://web.archive.org/web/20001018024013/http://lakewood.cc/ Contact Information]." ''Lakewood Church''. 2000-10-18. Retrieved on 2009-04-08.</ref><ref>"[https://web.archive.org/web/20030623055648/http://lakewood.cc/contactus.htm Contact Us]." ''Lakewood Church''. June 23, 2003.</ref> 迁移到更大的设施。<ref name=USA /> 2003年底，教会与休斯顿市签订了长期租约收购康柏中心体育场<ref name="A Sports Arena Gets Religion">{{cite news| title = A Sports Arena Gets Religion| work = New York Times| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2004/03/10/business/10prop.html?ex=1172552400&en=c8cb3279d9f71269&ei=5070| accessdate = 2007-02-25| first = Terry| last = Pristin| date = 2004-03-10| archive-date = 2009-04-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090424123021/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/03/10/business/10prop.html?ex=1172552400&en=c8cb3279d9f71269&ei=5070| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

湖木教会于2005年7月16日搬迁到休斯敦市中心西南59号高速公路边的康柏中心，拥有16,800座位，容量是旧堂的两倍。<ref name=USA /><ref>Lonsway, Brian. “Spiritual Summit.” CITE: The Houston Journal of Architecture. 74 (2008): 14-19.</ref> 2010年3月31日，休斯顿市议会出售该物业给湖木教会<ref>Bradley Olson and Moises Mendoza. "[http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/metropolitan/6937849.html City Council OKs sale of ex-Compaq to Lakewood] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/metropolitan/6937849.html |date=20100404102816 }}." ''Houston Chronicle''. 2010-03-31.</ref>。

==信仰==
湖木教会相信整本圣经是是由上帝所默示的，教会的教导是基于这个信仰。教会也持守[[三位一体|三位一体]], 以及承认基督死在十字架上并且复活的信条。

==事工==
湖木教会为不同年龄和婚姻状况的成员提供提供不同类型的事工：
* 儿童
* 中学生
* 青年
* 成人

[[Image:Lakewood1.jpg|thumb]]
教会每周的聚会在三一传播网和晨星电视网上广播。欧斯汀的布道也在100多个国家的电视上播放，每周估计有700万观众。<ref>{{cite web| title = No Politics From This Pulpit| work = Newsweek| url = http://www.newsweek.com/id/103290| accessdate = 2010-04-11| archive-date = 2009-07-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090729212923/http://www.newsweek.com/id/103290| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2002年，湖木教会开始了西班牙语事工。每周有两次西班牙语聚会，并将所有英语聚会翻译成西班牙语。西班牙语事工的每周出席人数约为6000人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espanol.lakewood.cc/pages/nuevo-aqui/horario-de-servicios.aspx|title=Horario de servicios|publisher=|accessdate=2014-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828013504/http://espanol.lakewood.cc/pages/nuevo-aqui/horario-de-servicios.aspx|archivedate=2012-08-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://espanol.lakewood.cc/pages/nuevo-aqui/marcos-witt.aspx|title=Marcos Witt|publisher=|accessdate=2014-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829161938/http://espanol.lakewood.cc/pages/nuevo-aqui/marcos-witt.aspx|archivedate=2012-08-29}}</ref>

